==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Ten years on the east side of the river, ten years on the west side of the river.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: shí nían hé dōng, shí nían hé xī

===Phrase===
'''[[十]][[年]][[河]][[东]]，[[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Prosperity and decline never last.
# (''idiom'') Life has its ups and downs.
# (''idiom'') Everything in life is cyclical.

===Alternate forms===
[[十]][[年]][[河]][[東]]，[[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

